{"tid":258843,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[HAWAII] 想問下夏威夷歐胡島有咩係必去/玩?","createTime":"2017-05-26T12:34:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T05:06:15.000Z","uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9982647c13c4859c4cfff85a6060ac371016584f","tid":258843,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T12:34:21.000Z","msg":"嚟緊6月中會去嗰度Grad Trip加探親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我去三聯/大眾都搵唔到有旅遊書係講夏威夷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以想問下各位巴絲有冇咩推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S.我上網搵到個叫Koalua Ranch嘅牧場係侏羅紀公園嘅拍攝場地都有興趣想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我想問下如果喺Waikiki嗰邊可以點去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跪求解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90027c1b3907144d1b5c7fac5b52412a3e8a2d2a","tid":258843,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:16:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3188eab1c1de3e082fe09af6aaaeae09e494cd18","tid":258843,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:11:00.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53630ab4ecd93880a3ad3a832052196481755fbc","tid":258843,"uid":20609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:30:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嚟緊6月中會去嗰度Grad Trip加探親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我去三聯/大眾都搵唔到有旅遊書係講夏威夷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以想問下各位巴絲有冇咩推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S.我上網搵到個叫Koalua Ranch嘅牧場係侏羅紀公園嘅拍攝場地都有興趣想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我想問下如果喺Waikiki嗰邊可以點去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跪求解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上痞客大把遊記<br />\n<br />\n岩岩五月返黎、你去幾多日？留多過一星期可以跳島玩<br />\n歐胡島最好租車方便好多！去北岸laniakea beach睇sea turtles, shark cove浮潛、Haleiwa小鎮行下、食giovanni's shrimp truck, Kia aina 食漢堡、仲有彩虹冰...呢度夠玩一日！<br />\n<br />\n另外珍珠港又玩一日啦、有時間去埋附近waikela premium outlet<br />\n<br />\nDiamond head行山、連埋blow hole、 世界十大最靚沙灘laniKai beach....其實大把野玩<br />\n<br />\n最緊要自己plan好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/122959_c263b6d03f3bfe4a335e784da949d325.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F122959_c263b6d03f3bfe4a335e784da949d325.jpg&h=59b1fdc5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/123003_330079b2468099598e7c896d52745520.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F123003_330079b2468099598e7c896d52745520.jpg&h=cbbf611c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/123007_7650d79ad5dff2935e0d26f36316eb49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F123007_7650d79ad5dff2935e0d26f36316eb49.jpg&h=be4f78dd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/123007_bd33b839fa080618b225581f44dd38dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http